#!/usr/bin/env testml


*in.up-words == *out


=== One lower-case word
--- in:  foo
--- out: Foo


=== Many lower-case words
--- in:  i like pie
--- out: I Like Pie


=== Various input cases
--- in:  Ingy dot Net haTes YAML
--- out: Ingy Dot Net Hates Yaml


=== Whitespace variations
--- in
foo    bar

    baz
--- out: Foo Bar Baz
